      <ul>
        <li> If <sourcexml>note</sourcexml> is the child of <sourcexml>text</sourcexml> then <sourcexml>note</sourcexml> and child <sourcexml>p</sourcexml> start-tags and end-tags (but not the content) are dropped, and 
              <sourcexml>note/p/text</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>inlinenote</targetxml> with attribute
          <sourcexml>note/@notetype</sourcexml> becoming
              <targetxml>inlinenote/@notetype</targetxml>.</li>
      </ul>      
    </p>
    </section>
