      <title>Source XML </title>
      <codeblock>

&lt;p&gt;
  &lt;text&gt;Some text of the paragraph...&lt;note type="editor-note"&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
            &lt;text&gt;This is an editorial note.&lt;/text&gt;
      &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/note&gt;...more text of the paragraph continuing after the note.&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

</codeblock>
      <title>Target XML</title>
      <codeblock>

&lt;p&gt;
  &lt;text&gt;Some text of the paragraph...&lt;inlinenote type="editor-note"&gt;This is an editorial note.&lt;/inlinenote&gt;...more text of the paragraph continuing after the note.&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

</codeblock>
